<!-- About us -->
<section id="about" class="section-3">
  <div class="container smaller">
    <div class="row text-center intro">
      <div class="col-12">
        <h2 class="super effect-static-text">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="text-max-800">
          Elliot Concept Agency is a web and media agency created for Entrepreneurs by Entrepreneurs and tech experts. We are the sister brand of Elliot for Water, an ethical search engine that donates water with your searches, and we are here to help brands around the world.
          For years, with our business, we have struggled with agencies that would promise us the world, charge us for the universe, and then made us chase them to actually get the bare minimum work. This situation forced us to take the long road and do everything by ourselves. The end result, though, is that we developed a search platform that has been used by 600,000 people, donated more than 1 million liters of water, and that has been featured in TV shows, radios, magazines, podcasts, and public events.
          We now feel that the time was right for us to give back to the entrepreneurial community and create an agency providing people with the quality of service they deserve, from Web Development to Online Marketing and Social Media. 
          To make this possible, we only work with a few selected brands, give them all the focus necessary, and elevate their online presence.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

